          <title>Popovich says he will not return to the Spurs this season, has hope of coaching in the future</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Gregg Popovich will not coach this season. He is not ruling out a comeback in the future. Popovich met with the San Antonio Spurs on Thursday, releasing a statement afterward to make his decision on this season — and hope for next season — public.]]></description>
